==Trivia==
*The character is a reference to Arthur Conan Doyle's character [[wikipedia:Sherlock_Holmes|Sherlock Holmes]].
*When your character observes that he has no shirt on, he will reply with "''No shirt, Sherlock''". This is a play on the phrase "''[[wiktionary:no shit, Sherlock|no shit, Sherlock]]''", an insult used when somebody points out an obvious fact.
*When using an item on Sherlock, he'll say: "That's nice, but... I don't really need one of those."

